@page "/about"

@* ==================================================
    ABOUT PAGE
    Provides information about the WorkSync application
    and its educational purpose.
================================================== *@
<h1>About WorkSync</h1>

<p>
    WorkSync helps company leaders and teams turn meeting decisions into clear,
    trackable work. It keeps workorders, assignments, owners, due dates, and
    follow-up items together so commitments remain visible between meetings.
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Track workorders and their progress</li>
    <li>Assign meeting action items to clear owners</li>
    <li>Review overdue and completed work</li>
    <li>Protect confidential follow-up items</li>
    <li>Prepare focused updates for the next team meeting</li>
</ul>

<p>
    This demo application uses sample company information only. Do not enter
    confidential business or personal information.
</p>
